          "$\\mathbf w\\cdot\\mathbf c=6-6-12=-12$, $|\\mathbf c|^2=9$, so $\\mathbf w_\\perp=(6,-3,-6)+\\tfrac{12}{9}(1,2,2)=(\\tfrac{22}{3},-\\tfrac13,-\\tfrac{10}{3})$.",
