          "This value is nonzero: if $\\vec a\\times\\vec b=\\vec 0$ then $\\vec a\\parallel\\vec b$, and with $\\vec c=-(\\vec a+\\vec b)$ all three would be collinear, impossible for three distinct unit vectors summing to zero. Hence $(B)$."
