          "$L$ passes through $(1,0,1)$: parametrize as $(1,0,1)+t(1,1,-2)$. The stated point $(\\alpha,1,\\gamma)$ forces $y=1\\Rightarrow t=1$, giving $\\alpha=2,\\ \\gamma=-1$, so $\\alpha-\\gamma=3$. Therefore $\\boxed{\\alpha-\\gamma=3\\ \\text{and}\\ l+m=2}$."
